   "source": "<ROUTINE WORKSHOP-F (\"OPTIONAL\" (RARG <>))\n <COND (<==? .RARG ,M-LOOK>\n\t<TELL\n\"The \" D ,WORKSHOP \" is equipped for mechanical repair work.\nIt contains assorted hand tools, machine tools, and spare parts.\" CR>)>>"
