   "endLine": 31,
   "source": "<ROUTINE BUZZER-WORD? (WORD)\n <COND (<QUESTION-WORD? .WORD> <RTRUE>)\n       (  <NUMBER-WORD? .WORD> <RTRUE>)\n       ( <NAUGHTY-WORD? .WORD> <RTRUE>)\n       (<EQUAL? .WORD ,W?ALL ,W?AGAIN ,W?G>\n\t<TELL \"(Sorry, but in this story you can't use the word \\\"\">\n\t<PRINTB .WORD>\n\t<TELL \"\\\".)\" CR>)>>"
