   "source": "<ROUTINE V-WAIT (\"OPTIONAL\" (NUM -1) (WHO <>) (INT <>) \"AUX\" VAL HR(RESULT T))\n\t #DECL ((NUM) FIX)\n\t <COND (<==? -1 .NUM>\n\t\t<SET NUM 10>\n\t\t<TELL ,I-ASSUME \" wait 10 turns.)\" CR>)>\n\t <SET HR ,HERE>\n\t <SETG WHO-WAIT 0>\n\t <COND (<NOT .INT> <TELL \"Time passes...\" CR>)>\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t\t <COND (<L? <SET NUM <- .NUM 1>> 0> <RETURN>)\n\t\t       (<SET VAL <CLOCKER>>\n\t\t\t<COND (<OR <==? .VAL ,M-FATAL>\n\t\t\t\t   <NOT <==? .HR ,HERE>>>\n\t\t\t       <SET RESULT ,M-FATAL>\n\t\t\t       <RETURN>)\n\t\t\t      (<AND .WHO <IN? .WHO ,HERE>>\n\t\t\t       <HAS-ARRIVED .WHO>\n\t\t\t       <RETURN>)\n\t\t\t      (<0? .NUM> <RETURN>)\n\t\t\t      (T\n\t\t\t       <SETG WHO-WAIT <+ ,WHO-WAIT 1>>\n\t\t\t       <COND (.INT <TELL\n\"Do you want to continue what you were doing?\">)\n\t\t\t\t     (T <TELL\n\"Do you want to keep waiting?\">)>\n\t\t\t       <COND (<NOT <YES?>> <RETURN>)\n\t\t\t\t     (T <USL>)>)>)\n\t\t       (<AND .WHO <IN? .WHO ,HERE>>\n\t\t\t<HAS-ARRIVED .WHO>\n\t\t\t<RETURN>)\n\t\t       (<AND .WHO <G? <SETG WHO-WAIT <+ ,WHO-WAIT 1>> 30>>\n\t\t\t<TELL D .WHO\n\" still hasn't arrived.  Do you want to keep waiting?\">\n\t\t\t<COND (<NOT <YES?>> <RETURN>)>\n\t\t\t<SETG WHO-WAIT 0>\n\t\t\t<USL>)\n\t\t       (T <USL>)>>\n\t <SETG CLOCK-WAIT T>\n\t .RESULT>"
